window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Investing in the stock market is a great way to build your wealth and make passive income. But knowing what information to trust and where to put your money may seem overwhelming to those of us who aren't skilled stockbrokers.&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Passive Income for Beginners</i> offers you with the strategic guidance and expertise needed to make informed investment choices. It removes the guesswork from investing by equipping you with everything you need to take control of your financial future.</p> <p>This audiobook gives you the tools to start investing, wisely and successfully, with:</p> <p></p> <ul> <li>A comprehensive overview of stock market fundamentals investing strategies</li> <li>Advice on purchasing, selling, owning, and diversifying</li> <li>Invaluable guidance on constructing your financial portfolio by investing in stock markets</li> </ul> <p>Even though the stock market is the core of the wealth of a country, and while it allows everyone to be a part owner in the world's biggest, most productive nations, it is not taught in American public colleges.</p> <p>But be advised: Frequently, the mainstream media misrepresents the stock market. They concentrate on making the news to sell copies interesting and dramatic.</p> <p>Frankly, boring investment is the best investment. It puts as much cash as you can afford and reinvests dividends in many businesses and continue to do so until retirement age is reached.</p> <p>This audiobook provides a good foundation for the beginning investor who is setting out to venture in the stock market. It informs you the basics of inventory market and investment strategies in simple English to deepen your investment literacy. You can discover it in this book if you are looking for good advice on what inventory to purchase and when to sell it.</p> <p>The best investment is not about attempting to find out what will occur tomorrow, next week, next month, or next year in the economy or markets.</p>"; 
